            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>beef mince</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, then add your<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and mix to combine – this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/953.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
