      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chilli is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with the zest<strong> </strong>and<strong> </strong>juice of<strong> half</strong> of your <strong>lime</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>zesty slaw dressing</strong></p><p>Finely grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
